line_1: As when some Musquet's Thunder has expell'd
line_2: Two loving Turtles from the verdant Field;

line_1: Rude to the world, like earth's first lord expell'd,
line_2: To climes unknown, from Eden's safer field;

line_1: To part from liberty, or be expell'd?
line_2: Can this be life, by gothic rules compell'd

line_1: Was, with the Partner of her Crime, expell'd
line_2: Our gen'ral Mother (who too soon rebell'd,)
